# Curated default sandbox skill names.
#
# Notes:
# - Blank lines and lines starting with # are ignored.
# - Each non-comment line is just a skill name, for example `ask-cascade`.
# - `03-skill-sync.sh` resolves names against the ordered sources in
#   `workspace/default-skills.sources.yaml`.
# - The first source containing `<source-root>/<skill-name>/SKILL.md` wins.

